Query String GET

=====================

<?php
$nama 	= "Toni Haryanto";
?>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<h1>Selamat Datang <?php echo $nama;?></h1>
</body>
</html>

====================================

Penggunaan nya : localhost/codepolitan/GET.php?nama=Muhammad Naufal&alamat=Bandung

<?php
$nama	= $_GET['nama'];
$alamat	= $_GET['alamat'];
?>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<h1>Selamat Datang <?php echo $nama;?></h1>
<h2>Alamat Kamu adalah di : <?php echo $alamat;?></h2>
</body>
</html>

=====================================

yang ini pake method get :

<html>
<body>
<form action="proses.php" method="get"> 
Nama: <input type="text" name="nama">
Alamat: <input type="text" name="alamat"><br><br>
<input type="submit" value="submit">
</form>
</body>
</html>

=============lanjutan nya ===================

<html>
<body>
Selamat Datang <?php echo $_GET["nama"]; ?><br>
Alamat Kamu: <?php echo $_GET["alamat"]; ?>
</body>
</html>


